{
  "texts": [
    "has fundamentally transformed various domains including academic writing practices.",
    "A GAI tool is a type of \"intelligent\" software program that can react to human text or voice inquiries by using natural language processing and deep learning techniques (Olujimi & Ade-Ibijola, 2023).",
    "These tools make use of the capabilities offered by LLMs.",
    "LLM are machine learning models trained on datasets consisting of a large amount of data allowing them to comprehend interpret and generate responses that are contextually relevant and coherent (Hadi et al., 2023).",
    "These tools generate different types of media, such as text, voice, images, and videos, some also offer advanced tasks such as image recognition, predictive modeling, and video analysis (Nakavachara et al., 2024)."
  ]
}